description: This skill asks the user a round of 3 questions about the author of the application. They are given one point for each question they get correct. At the end of the round the total score is given.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask terrell Trivia to Start game
Alexa, Ask Terrell Trivia to new game
Alexa, Ask Terrell Trivia to Start
name: Terrell Trivia
shortDescription: This is a spinoff of the trivia Skill.
